hadiths[66]{hadithnumber,text}:
876,ham duniya mein tamam ummaton ke baad honey ke bawajud qiyamat mein sabse aagey rahengey farq sirf ye hai ke kitab unhein ham se pahley di gaee thi. yahi (juma) unka bhi din tha jo tum par farz hua hai. lekin unka iske barey mein ikhtilaf hua aur Allah Taala ne hamein ye din bata diya isliye log usmein hamarey taabe hongey. yahood doosrey din hongey aur nasara teesrey din.
877,tum mein se jab koi shakhs Juma ki Namaz ke liye aana chahe to usey ghusl kar lena chahiye
878,"umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) Juma ke din khadey khutba de rahe they ke itney main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke agley sahaba muhajireen mein se aik buzurg tashrif laey (yani Usman (Raziallahu anhu)) umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha bhala ye kon sa waqt hai unhon-ne farmaya ke main mashghool ho gaya tha aur ghar wapas aatey hi azan suni , isliye main wuzu se zyada aur kuchh (ghusl ( na kar saka. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke wuzu bhi achchha hai. halanke aapko malum hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghusl ke liye farmatey they."
879,Juma ke din har baligh ke liye ghusl zaroori hai.
880,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Juma ke din har jawan par ghusl, miswak aur khushbu lagaanaa agar muyassar ho, zaroori hai. Amr bin -Sulaim ne kaha ke ghusl ke mutaalliq to main gawahi deta hun ke wo wajib hai lekin miswak aur khushbu ka ilm Allah Taala ko zyada hai ke wo bhi wajib hain ya nahi. lekin hadis mein isi tarah hai. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne farmaya ke Abu-Bakar bin-Munkadir Muhammad-bin-Munkadir ke bhai they aur unka naam malum nahi ( Abu-Bakar unki kunniyat thi) Bukair bin-Ashajj. Saeed-bin-abi-Hilal aur bahut se log unse riwayat kartey hain. aur Muhammad-bin-Munkadir unke bhai ki kunniyat Abu-Bakar aur abu-Adbullah bhi thi."
881,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs Juma ke din ghusle-janabat karke Namaz padhney jaey to maano usne aik oont ki qurbani di (agar awwal waqt masjid mein pahuncha (aur agar baad mein gaya to maano aik gaaey ki qurbani di aur jo teesrey number par gaya to maano usne aik seeng waley mendhey ki qurbani di aur jo koi chauthey number par gaya to usne maano aik murghi ki qurbani di aur jo koi paanchwein number par gaya us ne maano andaa Allah ki raah mein diya. lekin jab imam khutbe ke liye bahar aa jata hai to Farishtey khutba sunney mein mashghool ho jatey hain.
882,Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) Juma ke din khutba de rahe they ke aik buzurg (Usman (rz)) dakhil huey. umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke aap log Namaz ke liye aaney mein kyon der kartey hain. (awwal waqt kyon nahi aatey) aaney waley buzurg ne farmaya ke der sirf itni hui ke azan suntey hi maine wuzu kya (aur phir hazir hua) aap ne farmaya ke kya aap logon ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye hadis nahi suni hai ke jab koi Juma ke liye jaey to ghusl kar lena chahiye
883,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jo shakhs Juma ke din ghusl karey aur khub achi tarah se paakii hasil karey aur tel istemal karey ya ghar mein jo khushbu muyassar ho istemal karey phir Namaz Juma ke liye nikley aur masjid mein pahunch kar do aadmiyon ke darmyan na ghusey , phir jitni ho sakey nafl Namaz padhey aur jab imam khutba shuru karey to khamosh sunta rahe to iske us Juma se lekar doosrey Juma tak sarey gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain."
884,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hai ke Juma ke din bhale hi janabat (hambistari) na ho lekin ghusl karo aur apne sar dhoya karo aur khushbu lagaya karo. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ghusl ka hukm to theek hai lekin khushbu ke mutaalliq mujhey ilm nahi.
885,aap ne Juma ke din ghusl ke barey mein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hadis ka zikr kya to maine kaha ke kya tel aur khushbu ka istemal bhi zaroori hai? aap ne farmaya ke mujhey malum nahi.
886,"umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne (resham ka ( dhaarii daar joda masjide-Nabawi ke darwazey par biktaa dekha to kehney lagey ya Rasulullah ! behtar ho agar aap usey khareed lein aur Juma ke din aur wufood jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaein to unki mulaqat ke liye aap usey pehna karein. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke isey to wahi pahan sakta hai jiska aakhirat mein koi hissey na ho. iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas isi tarah ke kuchh jodey aaey to usmein se aik joda aap ne umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko ata farmaya, unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! aap mujhey ye joda pehna rahe hain halanke us se pahley utaarid ke jodey ke barey mein aap ne kuchh aisa farmaya tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine usey tumhen khud pahnney ke liye nahi diya hai, chunanche umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey apne aik mushrik bhai ko pehna diya jo makke mein rehta tha."
887,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar mujhey apni ummat ya logon ki takleef ka khayal na hota to main har Namaz ke liye unko miswak ka hukm de deta.
888,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main tum se miswak ke barey mein bahut kuchh keh chuka hun.
889,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab raat ko uthtey to munh ko miswak se khub saaf kartey.
890,"Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-abii-Bakar (eik martaba) aaey. unke hath mein miswak thi jisey wo istemal kya kartey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bimari ki haalat mein unse kaha Abdur-Rehman ye miswak mujhey de-dey. unhon-ne de di. maine iske sirey ko pahley todaa yani itni lakdi nikal di jo Abdur-Rehman apne munh se lagaya kartey they, phir usey chabaa kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko de diya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se daant saaf kiye aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt mere seeney par tek lagaey huey they."
891,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Juma ke din fajr ki Namaz main ( الم تنزيل‏ (aur (Sura Dahar) padha kartey they.
892,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki masjid ke baad sabse pahlaa Juma banu-abdul-Qais ki masjid mein hua jo Bahrain ke mulk Jawaasi mein thi.
893,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke tum mein se har shakhs nigahbaan hai aur Leis ne usmein ye zyadti ki ke Yunus ne bayan kya ke Ruzaiq-bin-Hakeem ne ibne-Shahab ko likha , un dinon main bhi waadii-ul-Quraa mein ibne-Shahab ke paas hi tha ke kya main Juma padha sakta hun. Ruzaiq (iila ke aas-paas) aik zameen par kheti karwaa rahe they. wahan Habsha wghaira ke kuchh log maujood they. us zamane mein Ruzaiq iila mein (Umar-bin Abdul-Azeez ki taraf se) Hakim they. ibne-Shahab (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne unhein likhwaayaa , main wahin sun raha tha ke Ruzaiq Juma padhaaein. ibne-Shahab Ruzeq ko ye khabar de rahe they ke Salim ne unse hadis bayan ki ke Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna. aap ne farmaya ke tum mein se har aik nigraan hai aur uske maa-tehton ke mutaalliq us se sawal hoga. imam nigraan hai aur us se sawal uski riaya ke barey mein hoga. insan apne ghar ka nigraan hai aur us se uski raiyat ke barey mein sawal hoga. aurat apne shauhar ke ghar ki nigraan hai aur us se uski raiyat ke barey mein sawal hoga. khaadim apne aaqa ke maal ka nigraan hai aur us se uski raiyat ke barey mein sawal hoga. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke mera khayal hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye bhi farmaya ke insan apne bap ke maal ka nigraan hai aur uski raiyat ke barey mein us se sawal hoga aur tum mein se har shakhs nigraan hai aur sabse uski raiyat ke barey mein sawal hoga."
894,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna ke tum mein se jo shakhs Juma padhney aaey to ghusl kare.
895,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke har baligh ke uper Juma ke din ghusl wajib hai.
896,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ham ( duniya mein) to baad mein aaey lekin qiyamat ke din sabse aagey hongey, farq sirf ye hai ke yahood w nasara ko kitab ham se pahley di gaee aur hamein baad mein. to ye din ( Juma ( wo hai jiske barey mein ahle-kitab ne ikhtilaf kya, Allah Taala ne hamein ye din batla diya (iske baad) doosra din ( hafta ( yahood ka din hai aur tesraa din ( itwaar ( nasara kaa. aap phir khamosh ho gaey."
897,iske baad farmaya ke har musalman par haq hai) Allah Taala ka (har saat (7) din mein aik din Juma mein ghusl karey jis main apne sar aur badan ko dhoey.
898,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ka har musalman par haq hai ke har saat (7) din mein aik din (juma) ghusl kare.
899,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aurton ko raat ke waqt masjidon mein aaney ki ijazat de diya karo.
900,umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki aik biwi thin jo subah aur isha ki Namaz jamat se padhney ke liye masjid mein aaya karti thin. unse kaha gaya ke bawajud us ilm ke ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) is baat ko makruh jantey hain aur wo ghairat mehsus kartey hain phir aap masjid mein kyon jati hain. is par unhon-ne jawab diya ke phir wo mujhey mana kyon nahi kar detey. logon ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki us hadis ki wjah se ke Allah ki bandiyon ko Allah ki masjidon mein aaney se mat roko.
901,Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne muazzan se aik baar barish ke din kaha ke (أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله‏) ke baad (حى على الصلاة) (namaz ki taraf aao ( na kehna balke ye kehna ke (صلوا في بيوتكم‏) (apne gharon mein Namaz padh lo ( logon ne is baat par tajjub kya to aap ne farmaya ke isi tarah mujh se behtar insan (rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ne kya tha. beshak Juma farz hai aur main makruh janta hun ke tumhen gharon se bahar nikal kar mitti aur keechad phisalwaan mein chalaaun.
902,"log Juma ki Namaz padhney apne gharon se aur Madina k aas-paas gaaun se (masjide-Nabawi mein) baari-baari aaya kartey they. log gardo-ghubaar mein chaley aatey, gard mein atey huey aur paseena mein sharaabor. is qadr paseena hota ke ruktaa nahi tha. usi haalat mein aik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum log us din (jum'a mein) ghusl kar liya kartey to behtar hota."
903,"unhon-ne Umra binte-Abdur-Rehman se Juma ke din ghusl ke barey mein poochha. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati thin ke log apne kaamon mein mashghool rahtey aur Juma ke liye usi haalat (mail-kuchail) mein chaley aatey, isliye unse kaha gaya ke kash! tum log (kabhii) ghusl kar liya kartey."
904,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Juma ki Namaz us waqt padhtey jab suraj dhal jata.
905,ham Juma sawerey padh liya kartey aur Juma ke baad aaraam kartey they.
906,"agar sardi zyada padtii to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz sawerey padh letey. lekin jab garmi zyada hoti to thandey waqt Namaz padhtey . aap ki murad Juma ki Namaz se thi. Yunus-bin-Bukair ne kaha ke hamein Abu-Khulda ne khabar di. unhon-ne sirf Namaz kaha, Juma ka zikr nahi kya aur Bashar-bin-Saabit ne kaha ke ham se Abu-Khulda ne bayan kya ke ameer ne hamein Juma ki Namaz padhai. phir Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zohar ki Namaz kis waqt padhtey they?"
907,"mein Juma ke liye ja raha tha. rastey mein abu-Abas (Raziallahu anhu) se meri mulaqat hui, unhon-ne kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai ke jiske qadam Allah ki raah mein ghubaar aalud ho gaey Allah Taala usey dozakh par haram kar dega."
908,aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke jab Namaz ke liye takbeer kahi jaey to daudtey huey mat aao balke (apni maamooli raftaar se) aao poorey itminan ke sath phir Namaz ka jo hissey (Imam ke saath) paalo usey padh lo aur jo reh jaey to usey baad mein pura karo.
909,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jab tak mujhey dekh na lo saff-bandii ke liye khadey na hua karo aur aahisatagi se chalnaa lazim kar lo.
910,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jisne Juma ke din ghusl kya aur khub paakii hasil ki aur tel ya khushbu istemal ki, phir Juma ke liye chala aur 2 aadmiyon ke beech mein na ghusaa aur jitni uski qismat mein thi, Namaz padhi, phir jab imam bahar aaya aur khutba shuru kya to khamosh ho gaya, iske us Juma se doosrey Juma tak ke tamam gunah bakhsh diye jaengey."
911,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se mana farmaya hai ke koi shakhs apne musalman bhai ko utha kar uski jagah khud baith jaey. maine Naafe se puchha ke kya ye Juma ke liye hai to unhon-ne jawab diya ke Juma aur ghair Juma sab ke liye yahi hukm hai.
912,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke zamaney mein Juma ki pehli azan us waqt di jati thi jab imam member par khutbe ke liye baithtey lekin Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke zamane mein jab musalmanon ki kasarat ho gaee to wo maqam Zauraa se aik aur azan dilwaaey lagey. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( farmatey hain ke Zauraa Madina ke bazar mein aik jagah hai.
913,Juma mein teesri azan Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ne badhaai jabke Madeene mein log zyada ho gaey they jabke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aik hi muazzan they. (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke daur mein) Juma ki azan us waqt di jati jab imam member par baithtaa.
914,"maine Muawiya bin abi Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha aap member par baithey, muazzan ne azan di ( الله أكبر الله أكبر‏ ( Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya ( الله أكبر الله أكبر‏ ( muazzan ne kaha ( أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله ( Muawiya ne jawab diya ( وأنا‏ (aur main bhi tauheed ki gawahi deta hun muazzan ne kaha (أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله‏) Muawiya ne jawab diya ( وأنا‏ (aur main bhi Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki risalat ki gawahi deta hun jab muazzan azan keh chuka to aap ne kaha haaziriin ! maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna usi jagah yani member par aap baithey they muazzan ne azan di to aap yahi farma rahe they jo tum ne mujh ko kehtey suna."
915,Juma ki dusri azan ka hukm Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ne us waqt diya jab namazi bahut zyada ho gaey they aur Juma ke din azan us waqt hoti jab imam member par betha karta tha.
916,"Juma ki pehli azan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke zamaney mein us waqt di jati thi jab imam member par baithtaa . jab Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ka daur aaya aur namaziyon ki tadaad badh gaee to aap ne Juma ke din aik teesri azan ka hukm diya, ye azan maqam Zauraa par di gaee aur baad mein yahi dastoor qaaim raha."
917,"kuchh log Sahal-bin-Sad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey. unka aapas main is par ikhtilaf tha ke mimbare-nabawii (Alaihissalam) ki lakdi kis darakht ki thi. isliye Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se iske mutaalliq malum kya gaya aap ne farmaya Allah gawah hai main janta hun ke mimbare-nabawii kis lakdi ka tha. pahley din jab wo rakha gaya aur sabse pahley jab is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baithey to main usko bhi janta hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar ki falan aurat ke paas jinka Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne naam bhi bataya tha. aadmi bheja ke wo apne badhaii ghulam se mere liye lakdi jod dene ke liye kahein. taake jab mujhey logon se kuchh kehna ho to is par betha karun chunanche unhon-ne apne ghulam se kaha aur wo Ghaaba ke jhaau ki lakdi se usey bana kar laya. Ansari khatun ne usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein bhej diya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey yahan rakhwaayaa. maine dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usi par (khadey ho kar) Namaz padhai. usi par khadey khadey takbeer kahi. usi par rukoo kya. phir ultey paon lautey aur member ki jad mein sajda kya aur phir dobara isi tarah kya jab aap Namaz se farigh huey to logon ko khitab farmaya, logo! maine ye isliye kya ke tum meri pairwi karo aur meri tarah Namaz padhni seekh lo."
918,aik khajoor ka tanaa tha jis par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tek laga kar khadey hua kartey they. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye member bin gaya (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us taney par tek nahi lagaayaa) to ham ne us se roney ki awaz suni jaisey das mahiney ki gaabhan ontni awaz karti hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne member se utar kar apna hath is par rakha (tab wo awaz rukii) aur Sulaiman ne Yahya se yun hadis bayan ki ke mujhey hafs-bin-Ubaidullaah-bin-Anas ne khabar di aur unhon-ne Jaabir se suna.
919,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne member par khutba detey huey farmaya ke jo Juma ke liye aaey wo pahley ghusl kar liya kare.
920,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey ho kar khutba detey they. phir baith jatey aur phir khadey hotey jaisey tum log bhi aaj kal kartey ho.
921,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik din member par tashrif farma huey aur ham sab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ird-gird baith gaey.
922,"main Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas gaee. log Namaz padh rahe they. maine (is be-waqt Namaz par tajjub se puchha ke) ye kya hai? Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne sar se aasman ki taraf ishara kya. maine puchha kya koi nishani hai? unhon-ne sar ke ishaare se haan kaha (kyonke suraj gehen ho gaya tha) Asma (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) der tak Namaz padhtey rahe. yahan tak ke mujh ko ghashii aaney lagi qareeb hi aik mashk mein pani bharaa rakha tha. main usey khol kar apne sar par pani dalney lagi phir jab suraj saaf ho gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz khatm kar di. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khutba diya. pahley Allah Taala ki uski shaan ke munasib tareef bayan ki. iske baad farmaya (امابعد)! itna farmana tha ke kuchh Ansari auratein shor karne lagein . isliye main unki taraf badhaii ke unhein chup karaun (taake Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baat achi tarah sun sakun magar main aap ka kalam na sun sakii) to puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya farmaayaa? unhon-ne bataya ke aap ne farmaya ke bahut si cheezein jo maine us se pahley nahi dekhi thin, aaj apni us jagah se maine unhein dekh liya. yahan tak ke jannat aur dozakh tak maine aaj dekhi. mujhey wahiy ke zariey ye bhi bataya gaya ke qabron mein tumhari aisi aazmaish hogi jaisey kaaney dajjal ke samney ya iske qareeb qareeb. tum mein se har aik ke paas farishta aaeyga aur poochhega ke to us shakhs ke barey mein kya aqeeda rakhta tha? momin ya ye kaha ke yaqin wala (Hishaam ko shak tha) kahega ke wo Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hain, hamarey paas hidayat aur waazeh dalaayel lekar aaey, isliye ham un par eman laaey, unki dawat qabool ki, unki ittaba (pairvi) ki aur unki tasdeeq ki. ab us se kaha jaeyga ke to to Saleh hai, aaraam se so jaa. ham pahley hi jantey they ke tera un par eman hai. Hisham ne shak ke izhar ke sath kaha ke raha munafiq ya shak karne wala to jab us se puchha jaeyga ke to us shakhs ke barey mein kya kehta hai to wo jawab dega ke mujhey nahi malum maine logon ko aik baat kehtey suna usi ke mutabiq maine bhi kaha, Hisham ne bayan kya ke Faatima-binte-Munzir ne jo kuchh kaha tha. maine wo sab yad rakha. lekin unhon-ne qabr mein munaafiqon par sakht azab ke barey mein jo kuchh kaha wo mujhey yad nahi raha."
923,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas kuchh maal aaya ya koi cheez aai. aap ne kuchh sahaba ko usmein se ata kya aur kuchh ko kuchh nahi diya. phir aapko malum hua ke jin logon ko aap ne nahi diya tha unhein iska ranj hua, isliye aap ne Allah ki hamd w tareef ki phir farmaya ( ammaa ba'd! ( ! Allah ki qasam! main kuchh logon ko deta hun aur kuchh ko nahi deta lekin main jisko nahi deta wo mere nazdeek unse zyada mahboob hain jinko main deta hun. main to un logon ko deta hun jinke dilon mein be-sabrii aur laalach paata hun lekin jinke dil Allah Taala ne khair aur be-niyaaz banaey hain, main un par bharosa karta hun. Amr-bin-Taghlab bhi un hi logon mein se hain. Allah ki qasam! mere liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye aik kalima surkh oonton se zyada mahboob hai."
924,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne raat ke waqt uth kar masjid mein Namaz padhi aur chand sahaba bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein Namaz padhney khadey ho gaey. subah ko un sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne doosrey logon se iska zikr kya chunanche (doosrey din) us se bhi zyada jama ho gaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey Namaz padhi. dusri subah ko iska charcha aur zyada hua phir kya tha teesri raat badi tadaad mein log jama ho gaey aur jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uthey to sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey Namaz shuru kar di. chothi raat jo aai to masjid mein namaziyon ki kasarat se til rakhney ki bhi jagah nahi thi. lekin aaj raat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye Namaz na padhai aur fajr ki Namaz ke baad logon se farmaya, pahley aap ne kalima shahadat padha phir farmaya, ( ammaa ba'd! )! mujhey tumhari us haziri se koi dar nahi lekin main is baat se dara ke kahin ye Namaz tum par farz na kar di jaey, phir tum se ye ada na ho sakey. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Yunus ne ki hai."
925,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz isha ke baad khadey huey. pahley aap ne kalima shahadat padha, phir Allah Taala ke laaiq uski tareef ki, phir farmaya ( ammaa ba'd! ( ! Zohri ke sath is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) abu-Muawia aur abu-Usama ne Hisham se ki, unhon-ne apne walid Urwa se uski riwayat ki, unhon-ne abu-Humed se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ( ammaa ba'd! ( ! aur abu-al-Yamaan ke sath us hadis ko Muhammad-bin-Yahyaa ne bhi Sufiyan se riwayat kya. usmein sirf ( ammaa ba'd! ( hai."
926,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey. maine suna ke kalima shahadat ke baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ( amma baad!)! Shuaib ke sath is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Muhammad-bin Waleed zubaidi ne Zohri se ki hai.
927,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par tashrif laey. member par ye aap ki aakhiri baithak thi. aap donon shaanon se chadar lapetey huey they aur sar Mubarak par aik patti baandh rakhi thi. aap ne hamd w sana ke baad farmaya logo! meri baat suno. chunanche log aap ki taraf kalaame-mubaarak sunney ke liye mutwajjeh ho gaey. phir aap ne farmaya ( ammaa ba'd! ( ! ye qabila Ansar ke log (aaney waley daur mein) tadaad mein bahut kam ho jaeinge to Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ummat ka jo shakhs bhi Hakim ho aur usey nafa w nuqsan pahunchaney ki taqat ho to Ansar ke nek logon ki neki qabool karey aur unke burey ki burai se darguzar kare.
928,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (Jum'a mein) 2 khutbey detey aur donon ke beech mein baithtey they. (khutba Juma ke beech mein ye baithna bhi masnoon tariqa hai).
929,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab Juma ka din aata hai to Farishtey jaame masjid ke darwazey par aaney walon ke naam likhtey hain, sabse pahley aaney wala oont ki qurbani dene waley ki tarah likha jata hai. iske baad aaney wala gaaey ki qurbani dene waley ki tarah, phir mendhey ki qurbani ka sawab rehta hai. iske baad murghi ka, iske baad andey kaa. lekin jab imam (khutba dene ke liye) bahar aa jata hai to ye Farishtey apne dafaatir band kar detey hain aur khutba sunney mein mashghool ho jatey hain."
930,aik shakhs aaya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Juma ka khutba de rahe they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke aey fulaan! kya tum ne (تحیۃ المسجد ki) Namaz padh li. usne kaha ke nahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya achchha uth aur 2 rakaat Namaz padh ley.
931,aik shakhs Juma ke din masjid mein aaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khutba padh rahe they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se puchha ke kya tum ne ( تحیۃ المسجد ki) Namaz padh li hai? aaney waley ne jawab diya ke nahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke utho aur 2 rakaat Namaz ( تحیۃ المسجد ( padh lo.
932,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Juma ka khutba de rahe they ke aik shakhs khada ho gaya aur arz kya ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maweshi aur bakriyan halaak ho gain (baarish na honey ki wjah se) aap dua farmaein ke Allah Taala barish barsaey. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne donon hath phailaey aur dua ki.
933,"aik martaba Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein qahat padaa, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khutba de rahe they ke aik dehati ne kaha ya Rasulullah ! janwar mar gaey aur ahal w ayaal daanon ko taras gaey. aap hamarey liye Allah Taala se dua farmaaein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne donon hath uthaaey, us waqt badal ka aik tukda bhi aasman par nazar nahi aa raha tha. us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai abhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hathon ko nichey bhi nahi kya tha ke pahadon ki tarah ghataa umad aai aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) abhi member se utrey bhi nahi they ke maine dekha ke barish ka pani Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki dadhi se tapak raha tha. us din iske baad aur mutwaatir agley Juma tak barish hoti rahi. (doosrey Juma ko) yahi dehati phir khada hua ya kaha ke koi doosra shakhs khada hua aur kaha ke ya Rasulullah! Imaaratein dheh gain aur janwar doob gaey. aap hamarey liye Allah se dua keejiye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne donon hath uthaey aur dua ki ke aey Allah ! ab dusri taraf barish barsa aur ham se rok de. aap hath se badal ke liye jis taraf bhi ishara kartey, udhar matla' saaf ho jata. Sara Madina taalaab ki tarah bin gaya tha aur qanaa ka nala mahina bhar bahtaa raha aur ird-gird se aaney waley bhi apne yahan bharpur barish ki khabar detey rahe."
934,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jab imam Juma ka khutba de raha ho aur to apne paas baithey huey aadmi se kahey ke ''chup reh'' to tu ney khud aik bekaar harkat ki.
935,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Juma ke zikr mein aik baar farmaya ke us din aik aisi ghadi aati hai jis mein agar koi musalman banda khada Namaz padh raha ho aur koi cheez Allah paak se maangey to Allah paak usey wo cheez zaroor deta hai. hath ke ishaarey se aap ne batlaya ke wo sa'at bahut thodi si hai.
936,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padh rahe they, itney mein ghalla laadey huey aik tijarati qaafila idhar se guzraa. log khutba chhod kar idhar chal diye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath kal baara aadmi reh gaey. us waqt Sura Juma ki ye aayat utri( وإذا رأوا تجارة أو لهوا انفضوا إليها وتركوك قائما‏ ) ""aur jab ye log tijarat aur khel dekhtey hain to uski taraf daud padtey hain aur aapko khada chhod detey hain.''"
937,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zohar se pahley 2 rakaat, iske baad 2 rakaat aur maghrib ke baad 2 rakaat apne ghar mein padhtey aur isha ke baad 2 rakatein padhtey aur Juma ke baad 2 rakatein jab ghar wapas hotey tab padha kartey they."
938,hamarey yahan aik aurat thi jo naalon par apne aik khet mein chuqandar botii. Juma ka din aata to wo chuqandar ukhaad laateen aur usey aik handi mein pakaatiin phir uper se aik muththii jo ka aata chhidak detiin. is tarah ye chuqandar gosht ki tarah ho jatey. Juma se waapsii mein ham unhein salam karne ke liye hazir hotey to yahi pakwaan hamarey aagey kar detiin aur ham usey chaat jatey. ham log har Juma ko unke us khaney ke aarzumand raha kartey they.
939,do-pahar ka sona aur do-pahar ka khana Juma ki Namaz ke baad rakhtey they.
940,"ham Juma sawerey padhtey, iske baad do-pahar ki neend letey they."
941,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Juma padhtey, phir do-pahar ki neend liya kartey they."
